documentation.text:
@title CompoundInterestERC20
 @dev This contract contains token-specific logic for investing ERC20 tokens into Compound protocol.
@dev Tells the address of the COMP token in the Ethereum Mainnet.
@dev Tells the address of the Comptroller contract in the Ethereum Mainnet.

@dev Claims Comp token received by supplying underlying tokens and transfers it to the associated COMP receiver.
 @param _markets cTokens addresses to claim COMP for.

attributes.text:
@title CompoundInterestERC20
 @dev This contract contains token-specific logic for investing ERC20 tokens into Compound protocol.
@dev Tells the address of the COMP token in the Ethereum Mainnet.
@dev Tells the address of the Comptroller contract in the Ethereum Mainnet.

@dev Claims Comp token received by supplying underlying tokens and transfers it to the associated COMP receiver.
 @param _markets cTokens addresses to claim COMP for.

devdoc.details: This contract contains token-specific logic for investing ERC20 tokens into Compound protocol.

claimCompAndPay(address[]).details: Claims Comp token received by supplying underlying tokens and transfers it to the associated COMP receiver.

params._markets: cTokens addresses to claim COMP for.

compAmount(address[]).details: Tells the amount of earned COMP tokens for supplying assets into the protocol that can be withdrawn. Intended to be called via eth_call to obtain the current accumulated value for COMP.

returns._0: amount of accumulated COMP tokens across given markets.

compToken().details: Tells the address of the COMP token in the Ethereum Mainnet.

comptroller().details: Tells the address of the Comptroller contract in the Ethereum Mainnet.

enableInterestToken(address,uint96,addre.details: Enables support for interest earning through specific cToken.

params._cToken: address of the cToken contract. Underlying token address is derived from this contract.
params._dust: small amount of underlying tokens that cannot be paid as an interest. Accounts for possible truncation errors.
params._interestReceiver: address of the interest receiver for underlying token and associated COMP tokens.
params._minInterestPaid: min amount of underlying tokens to be paid as an interest.

forceDisable(address).details: Last-resort function for returning assets to the Omnibridge contract in case of some failures in the logic. Disables this contract and transfers locked tokens back to the mediator. Only owner is allowed to call this method.

params._token: address of the invested token contract that should be disabled.

getModuleInterfacesVersion().details: Tells the module interface version that this contract supports.

interestAmount(address).details: Tells the current accumulated interest on the invested tokens, that can be withdrawn and payed to the interest receiver.

params._token: address of the invested token contract.

invest(address,uint256).details: Invests the given amount of tokens to the Compound protocol. Only Omnibridge contract is allowed to call this method. Converts _amount of TOKENs into X cTOKENs.

params._token: address of the invested token contract.

investedAmount(address).details: Tells the current amount of underlying tokens that was invested into the Compound protocol.

isInterestSupported(address).details: Tells if interest earning is supported for the specific underlying token contract.

returns._0: true, if interest earning is supported for the given token.

payInterest(address).details: Pays collected interest for the underlying token. Anyone can call this function. Earned interest is withdrawn and transferred to the specified interest receiver account.

params._token: address of the invested token contract in which interest should be paid.

setCompReceiver(address).details: Updates address of the accumulated COMP receiver. Can be any address, EOA or contract. Set to 0x00..00 to disable COMP claims and transfers. Only owner is allowed to call this method.

setDust(address,uint96).details: Updates dust parameter for the particular token. Only owner is allowed to call this method.

params._dust: new amount of underlying tokens that cannot be paid as an interest. Accounts for possible truncation errors.
params._token: address of the invested token contract.

setInterestReceiver(address,address).details: Updates address of the interest receiver. Can be any address, EOA or contract. Set to 0x00..00 to disable interest transfers. Only owner is allowed to call this method.

params._token: address of the invested token contract.

setMinCompPaid(uint256).details: Updates min COMP amount that can be transferred in single call. Only owner is allowed to call this method.

params._minCompPaid: new amount of COMP and can be transferred to the interest receiver in single operation.

setMinInterestPaid(address,uint256).details: Updates min interest amount that can be transferred in single call. Only owner is allowed to call this method.

params._minInterestPaid: new amount of TOKENS and can be transferred to the interest receiver in single operation.
params._token: address of the invested token contract.

transferOwnership(address).details: Changes the owner of this contract.

withdraw(address,uint256).details: Withdraws at least the given amount of tokens from the Compound protocol. Only Omnibridge contract is allowed to call this method. Converts X cTOKENs into _amount of TOKENs.

params._amount: minimal amount of tokens to withdraw.
params._token: address of the invested token contract.
